DIP Switch Plus: Privacy policy

Welcome to the DIP Switch Plus app for Android!

This is an Android app developed by Moran Senyor. 

As an avid Android user myself, I take privacy very seriously.
I know how irritating it is when apps collect your data without your knowledge.

I have not programmed this app to collect any information. All data (app preferences (like theme, etc.) and alarms) created by the you is stored on your device only, and can be simply erased by clearing the app's data or uninstalling it.

Yours sincerely,  
Moran Senyor
